snippet.title: MechWarrior 5 Mercenaries - MechCon 2018 Trailer
snippet.description:
MechWarrior 5 Mercenaries Trailer for MechCon 2018 in Vancouver

https://mechwarrior.com/mechcon

MechWarrior 5: Mercenaries is set for release in 2019! For more information, head to https://mw5mercs.com/

MechWarrior 5: Mercenaries will be available on December 10th, 2019!
Purchase on the Epic Games Store! 
https://www.epicgames.com/store/en-US/product/mechwarrior-5/home
